Hi Alejandro,



Just upgraded from 1.8.4 to 1.10.4 and realized the bindProperty method for
the association (selectedItem) will no longer work with the new base class
sap.ui.base.ManagedObject for sap.m.Select (since version 1.9.1). You could
call setSelectedItem each time the loadData is complete, but it sounds like
you may already be doing something similar.





    oModel.attachRequestCompleted(function() { 
     if (oSelect.isBound("items")) { 
     oSelect.unbindAggregation("items");
     } 
     oSelect.setSelectedItem(oModel.getProperty("/employee/country"));
     }); 



Cheers,

