Hi Chris,



you missed one important point in the renderer which enables the SAPUI5
framework to dispatch the event properly: writeControlData





     renderer : function(oRm, oControl) { 
     oRm.write('<li'); 
     oRm.writeControlData(oControl);
     oRm.write(">");
     oRm.writeEscaped(oControl.getTitle()); 
     oRm.write('</li>'); 
     }



It writes the ID plus some other information into the HTML element. The ID is
used to delegate event into the control behavior. By applying this change your
control will work.



Best regards,

Peter

